447
00:37:44,320 --> 00:37:45,930
Zhou Jiahei terlalu kejam.

448
00:37:46,600 --> 00:37:48,010
Dia tahu dirinya tidak bisa kabur,

449
00:37:48,930 --> 00:37:50,930
